WEBVTT

00:03:00.331 --> 00:03:04.976
And it's one of his first outings
as Vice President to an African country.

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.640
He doesn't quite know what to do,

00:03:06.664 --> 00:03:08.413
so he starts going around the crowd

00:03:08.437 --> 00:03:09.976
and starts talking to people

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.286
and he says to people
in this rather unique way,

00:03:12.310 --> 00:03:14.527
"How does it feel to be free?"

00:03:14.551 --> 00:03:17.273
And he's going around,
"How does it feel to be free?"

00:03:17.297 --> 00:03:18.884
"How does it feel to be free?"

00:03:18.908 --> 00:03:20.010
And then someone says,

00:03:20.034 --> 00:03:22.181
"How should I know? I come from Alabama."

00:03:22.205 --> 00:03:24.976
(Laughter)

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:28.404
And that was the 1950s.

